1
00:00:54,840 --> 00:00:55,679
Let me help you.

2
00:00:58,000 --> 00:00:59,280
Your hand is injured, isn't it?

3
00:00:59,560 --> 00:01:00,039
Let me do it.

4
00:01:08,280 --> 00:01:09,480
It's too early.

5
00:01:12,040 --> 00:01:12,959
You don't have to be so restrained.

6
00:01:13,079 --> 00:01:13,400
I won't look.

7
00:01:13,599 --> 00:01:14,159
You're awake.

8
00:01:14,719 --> 00:01:15,239
Xu Mengxi.

9
00:01:15,799 --> 00:01:16,120
Yes.

10
00:01:16,319 --> 00:01:17,120
I forgot to say it last time.

11
00:01:17,920 --> 00:01:18,599
Thank you

12
00:01:18,799 --> 00:01:19,359
for saving my life.

13
00:01:19,560 --> 00:01:20,120
You're welcome.

14
00:01:20,799 --> 00:01:22,719
I also have something to tell you.

15
00:01:23,439 --> 00:01:23,840
What?

16
00:01:25,280 --> 00:01:26,280
This is for Yan Ying.

17
00:01:26,920 --> 00:01:29,879
I stayed up late to help you rewrite the novel to save Yan Ying.

18
00:01:30,239 --> 00:01:31,599
But you don't even give me an egg.

19
00:01:31,599 --> 00:01:32,439
You are too much.

20
00:01:33,640 --> 00:01:34,560
This is yours.

21
00:01:35,319 --> 00:01:36,719
But I'm still quite touched.

22
00:01:37,480 --> 00:01:38,280
After all,

23
00:01:38,680 --> 00:01:40,599
you gave me your broken heart.

24
00:01:42,120 --> 00:01:42,879
You two go on a date.

25
00:01:42,879 --> 00:01:43,959
I have something to do and I'll leave now.

26
00:01:44,680 --> 00:01:45,359
Bye.

27
00:01:46,319 --> 00:01:46,640
Xu Chi,

28
00:01:51,799 --> 00:01:52,599
I love you.

29
00:01:53,319 --> 00:01:54,280
Are you crazy?

30
00:01:59,640 --> 00:02:00,359
I love you.

31
00:03:29,159 --> 00:03:30,879
I'll give you my identity

32
00:03:32,319 --> 00:03:33,159
and ask you to help me.

33
00:03:38,120 --> 00:03:38,680
What?

34
00:04:39,519 --> 00:04:40,319
Resign?

35
00:04:40,600 --> 00:04:41,040
Yes.

36
00:04:41,600 --> 00:04:42,000
Why?

37
00:04:42,480 --> 00:04:43,519
Thank you very much.

38
00:04:43,519 --> 00:04:45,279
You gave me a job

39
00:04:45,439 --> 00:04:46,560
when I first arrived.

40
00:04:47,079 --> 00:04:48,160
But since I'm staying,

41
00:04:48,319 --> 00:04:49,920
I must find my niche

42
00:04:49,920 --> 00:04:51,240
in this world.

43
00:04:51,639 --> 00:04:53,759
I've noticed that women here

44
00:04:54,160 --> 00:04:55,160
have more possibilities

45
00:04:55,279 --> 00:04:56,759
than in my world.

46
00:04:57,279 --> 00:04:58,879
They can showcase their talents

47
00:04:58,879 --> 00:05:00,480
in various industries.

48
00:05:01,319 --> 00:05:02,480
And I believe

49
00:05:02,480 --> 00:05:03,199
I, Yan Ying,

50
00:05:03,199 --> 00:05:04,360
am no less capable in every aspect.

51
00:05:04,800 --> 00:05:05,360
So,

52
00:05:05,680 --> 00:05:06,519
the world is vast,

53
00:05:07,120 --> 00:05:08,639
I can surely make it on my own,

54
00:05:08,920 --> 00:05:10,519
and find my own path.

55
00:05:11,800 --> 00:05:12,439
Maybe,

56
00:05:12,920 --> 00:05:14,480
I can even become

57
00:05:14,480 --> 00:05:15,319
a national heroine once more.

58
00:05:18,720 --> 00:05:19,319
Have you made up your mind?

59
00:05:19,879 --> 00:05:20,959
If you resign,

60
00:05:21,519 --> 00:05:22,959
we won't be together every day anymore.

61
00:05:23,360 --> 00:05:24,439
We can still be together here.

62
00:05:27,639 --> 00:05:28,360
Then,

63
00:05:28,879 --> 00:05:29,279
approved.

64
00:05:30,279 --> 00:05:33,319
Congratulations on graduating from my publishing house,

65
00:05:33,519 --> 00:05:34,399
and stepping into the real world.

66
00:05:35,319 --> 00:05:35,759
Oh, right.

67
00:05:36,720 --> 00:05:37,959
Xu Mengxi asked me to give you

68
00:05:41,680 --> 00:05:42,759
the termination letter.

69
00:05:43,279 --> 00:05:43,759
Hmm.

70
00:05:52,279 --> 00:05:53,160
Dear brother,

71
00:05:55,920 --> 00:05:56,959
I've reached the highest point

72
00:05:57,279 --> 00:05:58,600
I can touch

73
00:05:58,600 --> 00:05:59,839
in the path of being a writer.

74
00:06:00,920 --> 00:06:01,839
So I've decided

75
00:06:02,199 --> 00:06:02,879
to retire from writing.

76
00:06:03,560 --> 00:06:04,399
and stop writing.

77
00:06:05,160 --> 00:06:06,079
From today,

78
00:06:06,439 --> 00:06:07,959
I'm starting my second life.

79
00:06:08,720 --> 00:06:09,959
I want to be an internet celebrity.

80
00:06:13,839 --> 00:06:14,480
Besides,

81
00:06:15,560 --> 00:06:17,040
I've prepared a surprise for you.

82
00:06:24,480 --> 00:06:25,279
Xu Chi,

83
00:06:26,079 --> 00:06:27,079
you're trending on Weibo.

84
00:06:30,879 --> 00:06:31,519
What?

85
00:06:33,480 --> 00:06:34,920
I should return the light I borrowed from you.

86
00:06:36,879 --> 00:06:37,360
Now,

87
00:06:39,079 --> 00:06:40,160
you can be yourself.

88
00:06:57,959 --> 00:06:58,480
Yan Ying,

89
00:06:59,360 --> 00:07:00,240
I found you.
